social_posts.post_text: My longtime friend @kirtsilver and fellow @starbritecolors proteam bro has a client who recently became an amputee, and asked if I could give him some encouragement. I’m honored to have this happen a lot and I’m always more than happy to help a new amputee see the light at he end of the tunnel. The magical thing here is, Kirt sent me a message back lifting me and my spirits up. So I want to take a moment thank him and all of the countless humans who reach out to me on an almost daily basis to let me know the difference I’ve made in this world. Helping people is why I deliver motivation, love, and support. It’s why I became a speaker, a coach, and it’s what keeps me going in the right direction especially on the days I don’t want to. So much love to Kirt and everyone else who reached out for love, support, guidance, coaching, and everything else. I appreciate every single one of you and all the energy y’all bring 💖💖💖
